data.name: richTxtBoxRules.Text
data.value:
There are three players on the game field - the Pacman and two ghosts. The Pacman purpose is to eat all yellow dots on the board. Ghosts goal is to catch th Pacman.
If any ghost meets the Pacman the result will be always the same. The Pacman will Die :( But the Pacman has three lives, so he can try to win again.
The game is over in two cases: When Pacman win (there are no more yellow dots on the field) When Pacman loose (he'd been eated three times).
Good Luck!
